# Changelog

## [Unreleased]
### Added
- Allow configuring ObjectLocker on controller.
- Add retries to the controller.
- Add Prometheus recorder implementation.
- Add Metrics recorder.
- Add Controller.
- Add ListerWatcher.
- Add Storage.
- Add Handler.

### Changed
- Store and ListerWatcher now receive a context.

